# Travel Tour Agency - Project Plan

## Project Overview
A modern, marketing-focused frontend for a travel agency promoting group tours and trips to Turkey. Built with Next.js 14+, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui components.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui
- **Maps**: Mapbox GL JS
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Images**: Unsplash API or placeholder images

