## Features Breakdown

### 1. Landing Page (`/`)
- **Hero Section**: Large banner with CTA, hero image
- **About Us Section**: Brief company introduction
- **Featured Trips**: Carousel of 4-6 featured trips
- **Why Us Section**: 5 cards (matching example design)
  - Persoonlijk reisadvies
  - Begeleiding bij elke stap
  - Aangesloten bij garantiefondsen
  - Vijf sterren bij Google
  - De mooiste reizen
- **Footer**: Social links, navigation, contact info

### 2. Trip Types
- **Groepsreizen** (`/reizen/groepsreizen`)
- **Maatwerk Reizen** (`/reizen/maatwerk`)
- **Self Drives** (`/reizen/self-drives`)
- **City Trips** (`/reizen/citytrips`)

### 3. Regions (Regio's)
- Centraal Anatolië
- Egeïsche Kust
- Mediterrane Rivièra
- Oost-Turkije
- Zuidoost & Mesopotamië

### 4. Trip Detail Page (`/reizen/[type]/[slug]`)
Based on letstravel.nl structure:
- Hero section with trip name, duration, price
- Overview section
- Day-by-day itinerary
- "Wat kan ik bezoeken?" (What can I visit?) section
- "Reis is inclusief" (Included) section
- "Reis is exclusief" (Excluded) section
- Image gallery
- CTA buttons (Reis aanvragen, Meer informatie)
- Map showing route/destinations

### 5. Filtering System
- Filter by trip type
- Filter by region
- Combined filters
- Search functionality
- Sort options (price, duration, popularity)

### 6. Mapbox Integration
- Interactive map showing Turkey regions
- Clickable regions to filter trips
- Trip detail pages show route/destinations

## Data Structure

### Trip Object
```typescript
interface Trip {
  id: string;
  slug: string;
  title: string;
  subtitle: string;
  type: 'groepsreizen' | 'maatwerk' | 'self-drives' | 'citytrips';
  region: string;
  duration: number; // days
  price: number; // from price
  priceNote: string;
  bestTravelTime: string;
  departureCity: string;
  images: string[];
  overview: string;
  highlights: string[];
  itinerary: DayPlan[];
  included: string[];
  excluded: string[];
  featured: boolean;
  coordinates?: [number, number]; // for map
  route?: [number, number][]; // for route display
}

interface DayPlan {
  day: number;
  title: string;
  description: string;
  locations?: string[];
}
```

